<p> <strong id="tp">Transcript Procedure</strong></p>
<p> Students are responsible for reading and complying with directives appearing as comments on their academic transcript. A student who fails to comply with comment instructions may be asked to withdraw from the program. All comments are removed from the transcript at the time of graduation.</p>
